RELATION CUSTOMER IS
  KEY CUS.NUM, ACTG.SYS.TYP, DSTART
  DATA CUS.DIST, CUS.AREA, CUS.REG, DSTOP, CUS.DET.CODE, INV.CODE, CUS.SLSM,
    MIN.CODE, PO, PO.MAX, PO.DSTART, PO.DSTOP, VAR.PRIC, DFLT.PRIC

